Pat Healy (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Healy_(actor) 0 Pat Healy (born September 14, 1971) is an American film and television actor perhaps best known for his leading roles in Great World of Sound, Compliance, The Innkeepers and Cheap Thrills. He directed his first feature film, Take Me, in 2017.
